---
// Logo preview page for evaluation
---
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Logo Sketches - Priap.OS</title>
  <style>
    body {
      background: #1A1A2E;
      color: #E8E4D9;
      font-family: system-ui, sans-serif;
      padding: 2rem;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 3rem;
    }
    h1 {
      font-family: Georgia, serif;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      color: #00F5D4;
    }
    .logo-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 2rem;
      max-width: 900px;
    }
    .logo-card {
      background: rgba(0,245,212,0.05);
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,245,212,0.2);
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 1rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .logo-card img {
      width: 200px;
      height: auto;
    }
    .logo-card h3 {
      margin: 1rem 0 0.5rem;
      color: #7B2CBF;
    }
    .logo-card p {
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      opacity: 0.8;
    }
    .notes {
      max-width: 700px;
      background: rgba(123,44,191,0.1);
      border-left: 3px solid #7B2CBF;
      padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }
    .notes h2 {
      color: #7B2CBF;
      margin-top: 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>LOGO SKETCHES</h1>

  <div class="logo-grid">
    <div class="logo-card">
      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/logo/logo-v1-oracle-eye.svg`} alt="V1: Oracle Eye">
      <h3>V1: Oracle Eye Pyramid</h3>
      <p>Classic Eye of Providence with leek as pupil inside pyramid. Most "Greek mysticism" vibes.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="logo-card">
      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/logo/logo-v2-leek-circuit.svg`} alt="V2: Leek Circuit">
      <h3>V2: Leek + Circuit</h3>
      <p>Central leek with circuit traces emanating. Eye embedded in the leek body. Most "tech" forward.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="logo-card">
      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/logo/logo-v3-minimal-eye.svg`} alt="V3: Minimal Eye">
      <h3>V3: Minimal Eye</h3>
      <p>Clean almond eye shape with geometric leek pupil. Most versatile for small sizes.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="notes">
    <h2>My Analysis</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>V1</strong>: Strong brand recognition, but pyramid might feel too "illuminati" rather than Greek. Wordmark works well.</li>
      <li><strong>V2</strong>: Very cyberpunk, circuit traces are cool. Eye-in-leek is unique but might be too busy for small sizes.</li>
      <li><strong>V3</strong>: Cleanest, scales best, but loses some personality. Good for favicon.</li>
    </ul>
    <p><strong>Recommendation</strong>: Hybrid - V1's pyramid structure + V3's minimal execution. Or V2's circuit aesthetic with V3's cleaner shapes.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
